# SCORE-Variance-Engine v1.2

A high-performance financial variance and mean-reversion engine designed for the **FASE Project**.

## Features
- **Native RSS Pipeline:** Real-time sentiment injection to weight variance thresholds.
- **Dynamic Recoil Logic:** Automated mean-reversion detection during high-volatility events.
- **Bulk Processing:** Optimized for large-scale analysis of high-beta sectors (e.g., Energy/WTI).
- **Architecture:** Lead AI Architect design focusing on speed and "Alpha" extraction.

## Usage
